P:120/120<br />\n使用武器：大劍（雙手劍）- 熟練度：2<br />\n習得技能：二連斬，重擊<br />\n物品：訓練所專用藥水*8<br />\n<br />\n屬性：<br />\nSTR:15<br />\nAGI:11<br />\nVTI:25<br />\nINT:11<br />\nDEX:12<br />\nLUK:11<br />\n<br />\n（已將屬性點數分配完成，重點分配VTI，其次STR，最後DEX，能力方面取其血量和防禦優先，其次力量，最後靈巧。）<br />\n<br />\n（*當屬性VTI每10進增長會增加100HP，而等級提升1等級亦會增加100HP；屬性INT每10進增長時會增加100MP，而等級提升1等級會增加20MP。）<br />\n<br />\n小雲：由於你選擇注重防禦，武器仍然使用大劍。接下來，請你選擇任務。<br />\n<br />\nA: 擊倒野獸-野豬王<br />\nB: 與訓練所騎士長修練<br />\n<br />\n*根據所選擇任務分配完成後額外獎勵"},{"pid":"0798fb6e9392865303cbd58986c3a6fe79da2588","tid":922258,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"A: 擊倒野獸-野豬王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aed1b255db03bcf14e45568a3c466f8076f2c25","tid":922258,"uid":184845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"live左<br />\n加油呀先生R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9e4dba933714ae8ddfa447fac9a22d20aef8ee","tid":922258,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aed1b255db03bcf14e45568a3c466f8076f2c25","tid":922258,"uid":184845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"live左<br />\n加油呀先生R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"等食燒豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c096a4ed00df10fc40db9b00208dac54289c04c9","tid":922258,"uid":42533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aed1b255db03bcf14e45568a3c466f8076f2c25","tid":922258,"uid":184845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"live左<br />\n加油呀先生R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class